---
title: Falafel Flatbreads and Halloumi Fries with Fresh Pomegranate Salad and Yoghurt Tahini Dressing
description: We love good Falafel Flatbreads and Halloumi Fries and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chermoula-falafel-flatbreads-9ac6b06c-2fb382cc.jpg
